multimedia/couchpotato includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/couchpotato

TO START COUCHPOTATO ON BOOT:
echo 'couchpotato_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/couchpotato start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:5050/

